OL,4,CU-turn on housing benefit for young
OL,5, Ministers have reversed a 2014 move
OL,6, stopping people under the age of 21
OL,7, automatically getting housing benefit.
OL,9,FWork and Pensions Secretary Esther
OL,10,FMcVey said the change would "reassure
OL,11,Fall young people that housing support
OL,12,Fis in place if they need it".
OL,14,FIt was estimated that 10,000 young
OL,15,Fpeople would have been hit by the move.
OL,17,FLabour welcomed the move which it says
OL,18,Fwas one of its 2017 manifesto promises,
OL,19,Fbut added that young people still
OL,20,Fstruggle to get affordable housing.
